title: KT TOES DON'T TOUCH GROUND Foldable Free Standing Pull Up Bar Stand Sturdy Power Tower Workout Station For Home Gym Strength Training Adjustable Pullup Fitness Equipment Multifunctional Exercise Rack
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
features: Workout Comfort: Designed by Mr. Khanh Trinh, who has over 15 years of experience in Fitness & Calisthenics, the KT Pull Up Bar provides comfort and quality for pull-ups and chin-ups. The height can be adjusted across multiple levels from 46.45'' to 101.57'' (118 to 258cm) without needing a spanner, allowing for full-body stretches and swings. Suitable for users up to 6.56 ft (200cm) and 485 lbs (200kg), it supports various workouts, including kipping pull-ups, muscle-ups, and more.

Near-Perfect Stability and Durability: The KT Pull Up Bar achieves near-perfect stability, minimizing wobble by 93%. Designed by an experienced expert-who always knows what the user wants, it showcases formidable strength and durability. It can sustain up to 771.6 lbs (350kg), providing a stable platform for the most vigorous exercises, ensuring minimal wobble and maximum efficiency

Ultra-Light and Highly Portable: Unlike traditional bulky steel stands, the KT1.1520-ALU pull-up bar stand is crafted from high-strength aluminum alloy, weighing just 26.45 lbs (11 kg). This lightweight construction doesn’t compromise on strength, offering a max load capacity of 771.6 lbs. It’s easy to move and store: Whether you’re working out indoors or outdoors, you can take this stand wherever you need it with minimal effort

Weatherproof Durability: Unlike most indoor-only equipment, the KT1.1520-ALU chin-up bar is crafted from high-strength aluminum and finished with a weather-resistant powder coating. It effortlessly withstands rain, sun, and snow. Enjoy peace of mind knowing this durable stand can withstand the elements and provide reliable performance for up to 30 years, no matter where you set it up

Safe For All Your Family Members: Unlike some other Pull Up Dip Stations with narrow footprint, KT Freestanding Pull Up Bar is much more widely so your shin or knee will never hit on the frame as you drop back down from pull ups. You will never feel cramped in it even if you’re a big person. The handle bar width is 39.37’’, allows you to hold wide or narrow as your fitness purpose. Its handle bar also NEVER falls down suddenly like some kinds of doorway pull up bars

Foldable And Versatile: The KT Portable Collapsible Chin Up Bar can be folded up quickly in 08 seconds, allows you to free up the space after exercise. You can use KT Kipping Pull Up Bar Tower anywhere as per your training regime (indoor, outdoor, garage, playground, bedroom, gym room or office). It can be used well with Aerial Yoga Hammock, Swing Chair, Punching Bag, Calisthenics Gymnastic Rings, Resistance Bands

Consistent Quality: We maintain strict quality control from production to release. The KT Gym Fitness Pullup Bars are manufactured on semi-automated lines, with precise welding and painting by programmed robots. Expect a high-quality product as advertised, built to last for years of reliable use

title: Garren Fitness Maximiza Plus Pull Up Bar – Wide Doorway Pullup Bar/Chinup Bar with 3 Sets of Screw-in Door-Mounts – Only for Doors Wider Than 35 Inches (Adjustable Width 35 to 50 Inches)
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
description: For Wide doorways (35 to 50 Inches Adjustable Width) - ’Pull Up to Fitness’ with the Maximiza Plus Pull-Up Bar by Garren FitnessThe Maximiza Plus Pull-up Bar is a perfect addition to any fitness routine for upper-body strength and toning. Its versatile uses include pull-ups, chin-ups, hanging leg raises, sit-ups and crunches. As you gain strength, it is easy to add more variations and difficulty into your Pull-up Bar exercises. With the Maximiza, you need minimal space in your house to do highly effective bodyweight exercises. The heavy-duty chrome steel bar and the multiple screw-in door mounts provide safety and stability while giving you the flexibility to move it to different places or heights. The non-slip extra-long foam grips provide a firm grip and extra comfort to minimize hand fatigue. The Maximiza Doorway Pull Up Bar is adjustable to fit wide doorways between 35 and 50 inches when extended. It comes with 3 sets of heavy-duty door mounts which can be screwed into up to 3 wooden doorframes in your house. Mounting Note: Always secure to the doorframe with the provided screw-in door mounts.The maximum installation height and bodyweight supported will vary depending on the individual circumstances including required usage, mounting method and the doorframe. We always recommend using the Heavy-duty door mounts for pullups and chin-ups. Maximum weight for typical installations is 330 lbs / 150kg. Safety Note: Each time the bar is used, you should cautiously apply your weight to it during the first few exercises to confirm that it is secure and will safely hold your weight.
features: Use for Wide Doors (Over 35 Inches): The pull ups bar is adjustable to fit Wide doorways between 35 and 50 inches

Screw-In Door Mounts for Safety: Heavy-duty chrome steel pull-up bar and door mounts provide great support and safety - Holds up to 330 lbs (150kg) when properly mounted using supplied screw-in door brackets. Note: Always use the provided screw-in door mounts and the locking screws

Build Upperbody Strength: Tone and strengthen your back, arms, shoulders and abs muscles for the perfect upperbody workout. It's the perfect pullup exercise equipment for your own gym in the home, garage or the office
Versatile Uses: Use for many exercises including pullups, chin-ups, hanging leg raises, situps and crunches (Note: Not to be used for other gymnastic moves or as a children's plaything)
Comfortable Hand-Grips: Non-slip extra-long foam grips for extra comfort to minimize hand fatigue during that tough pullup workout
Different Locations: the 3 sets of screw-in door mount kits give flexibility to move to different doorways or put at different heights
Does NOT fit standard doorways: please measure your doorway to ensure that it is between 35 and 50 inches wide

description: Product Description TOTAL UPPER BOOY WORKOUT BAR Turn your doorway into a home gym. The KAKICLAY pull up bar is a multi-function exercise bar you can use to do pull-ups, chin-ups, push-ups, sit-ups, dips, arm and shoulder exercises- every exercise you need to build a powerful upper body! The KAKICLAY gym uses your body's own resistance to deliver powerful results fast. It strengthens and tones your biceps, triceps, chest, back, shoulders and abs. It instantly attaches to or removes from your door frame with no drilling or tools required, and the heavy duty steel construction supports up to 440 ibs! Now it's easy to get the strong, lean body you always wanted, right at home.  FEATURES:  (1)Latest Unique Design & Multiple Strength Training  (2)No Drillings & No tools & No fasteners (3)Heavy Duty Steel Construction & Stability (4)Attaches & Removes from Door Frame in Seconds Important Tips Before Ordering (1)Maximum weight that the doorframe can support. (2)Slip-in design fits standard doorways. (3)Can holds up to 440LBS man for long term use.  (4)Aluminum alloy doors and glass doors cannot be installed.
features: 【Multifunctional Home Gym】The latest pull-up bar supports push-ups, sit-ups, pull-ups, pull-ups, arm curls, arm and shoulder exercises, and other exercises. You can easily switch between multiple exercises without other fitness door bars to help you build strong upper body and core muscles.

【Ergonomic Design】KAKICLAY Pull Up Bar is an ideal upper body exercise equipment with three grip positions, narrow, wide, and neutral. The handle is equipped with ergonomic comfort foam for a comfortable grip, non-slip and wear resistance to protect your wrists and relieve fatigue during exercising.

【Door Frame Protection】The top of this pull-up bar is equipped with thickened foam to protect the top of the door frame from damage. Also the pull-up bar is equipped with foam handles on the outside and inside, which can effectively prevent damage to the sides of the door frame.

【Easy Installation】Our door frame puller is simple to install with safety brackets, safety manuals and assembly tools, making it easy to install and remove in seconds. It uses leverage against the door frame, so there is no drilling required and no damage to the door. The pull up bar is 36.5" long and fits any standard door opening from 24" to 32" wide and 4" to 6.3" deep. It holds up to 440 lbs.

【No Worry Buying】Before using the upper body workout bar tug down on the grips to make sure the unit is securely installed into door frame. Any problems please feel free to contact us by email, we will solve it for you as soon as possible. And we offer 24 months manufacturer’s warranty.

description: Product Description TOTAL UPPER BOOY WORKOUT BAR Turn your doorway into a home gym. The KAKICLAY pull up bar is a multi-function exercise bar you can use to do pull-ups, chin-ups, push-ups, sit-ups, dips, arm and shoulder exercises- every exercise you need to build a powerful upper body! The KAKICLAY gym uses your body's own resistance to deliver powerful results fast. It strengthens and tones your biceps, triceps, chest, back, shoulders and abs. It instantly attaches to or removes from your door frame with no drilling or tools required, and the heavy duty steel construction supports up to 440 ibs! Now it's easy to get the strong, lean body you always wanted, right at home.  FEATURES:  (1)Latest Unique Design & Multiple Strength Training  (2)No Drillings & No tools & No fasteners (3)Heavy Duty Steel Construction & Stability (4)Attaches & Removes from Door Frame in Seconds Important Tips Before Ordering (1)Maximum weight that the doorframe can support. (2)Slip-in design fits standard doorways. (3)Can holds up to 440LBS man for long term use.  (4)Aluminum alloy doors and glass doors cannot be installed.
features: 【Multifunctional Home Gym】The latest pull-up bar supports push-ups, sit-ups, pull-ups, pull-ups, arm curls, arm and shoulder exercises, and other exercises. You can easily switch between multiple exercises without other fitness door bars to help you build strong upper body and core muscles.

【Ergonomic Design】KAKICLAY Pull Up Bar is an ideal upper body exercise equipment with three grip positions, narrow, wide, and neutral. The handle is equipped with ergonomic comfort foam for a comfortable grip, non-slip and wear resistance to protect your wrists and relieve fatigue during exercising.

【Door Frame Protection】The top of this pull-up bar is equipped with thickened foam to protect the top of the door frame from damage. Also the pull-up bar is equipped with foam handles on the outside and inside, which can effectively prevent damage to the sides of the door frame.

【Easy Installation】Our door frame puller is simple to install with safety brackets, safety manuals and assembly tools, making it easy to install and remove in seconds. It uses leverage against the door frame, so there is no drilling required and no damage to the door. The pull up bar is 36.5" long and fits any standard door opening from 24" to 32" wide and 4" to 6.3" deep. It holds up to 440 lbs.

【No Worry Buying】Before using the upper body workout bar tug down on the grips to make sure the unit is securely installed into door frame. Any problems please feel free to contact us by email, we will solve it for you as soon as possible. And we offer 24 months manufacturer’s warranty.

Can the screws bear this weight? Will it break? 
This situation has been mentioned many times in reviews of other brands. Don't worry, it's very sturdy and my 260lbs weight has no problem at all. 
Can I mount it on a concrete wall? 
Yes, in the product I received, in addition to the screws for wooden beams, there were also special expansion screws for cement wall, which I used to install my pull up bar on the cement wall. 
Is it difficult to assemble the wall pull up bar? 
It only takes half an hour to install this pull up bar according to the instructions. 
What makes this Heavy Duty Chin Up Bar better than the others and how many workouts are there? 
It's made of heavy-duty alloy steel that can withstand 600 pounds of force and can wide, narrow, neutral, ball finger and hammer grip, and it versatile for resistance training, suspension training, and strength training.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Brand Introduction 
Matrix-Athletic has been focused on home fitness system for 20 years, whose products can be applied to home, office, public areas, fitness training institutions and other environments, and can be installed interior walls, exterior walls, basements, garages, office gyms and other areas. Their products have multifunction, modularization, easy installation, saving space, economy and other characteristics. The company pursues the concept of scientific and professional sustainable development of products, to create a good fitness experience for users through technological upgrading and innovation, and help more people to enhance their physique, shape their body and achieve their fitness goals through our products. 
Wall Mount 
1、Wall mounting, Innovative design; 
2、It does not occupy the ground space, and will solve the fitness dilemma of small households and narrow space; 
3、Strong stability prevents it from shaking or sliding, and can give users a safe and reliable training experience; 
Foldable Dip Station 
Humanized design, when you finish fitness, the Dip Station module can be folded to prevent bumping and provide you with more activity space; 
Organizer Function 
Elastic bands, resistance bands, suspension training straps, and yoga straps can be stored by hanging them on a horizontal bar. 
Foam Handles 
Anti-slip, comfortable, with good cushioning and anti-sweat; 

Description of Installation Wall Type 
1、Please mount on concrete wall, brick wall and wood stud wall(Stud Spacing(on center) : 24″ ). 
2、Mounting wall thickness should exceed 4″. 
Wall Mounting Dimension 
Installation space 
Set-Up Dimensions Approx. (W x H x D) : 51″ x 52″ x 26″ ； 
Warm Reminder: 
1、Please read the installation instructions before installation. 
2、If there is a problem with the mounting or you encounter a wall situation that does not fit the mounting, Please consult online.

title: Sportneer Pull Up Bar: Adjustable Width Locking Mechanism Chin up Bar without Screws - Strength Training Pull-up Bar for Doorway with Non-slip Comfort for Home Gym Upper Body Workout
inStockText: In Stock  Only 1 left in stock - order soon.
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
features: Before purchasing, ensure your door frame width is between 30-37.4 inches (76 to 95 cm). This chin up bar is not suitable for frames outside this range. The door frame must be wider than the anti-slip pads at both ends of the bar

To ensure safety, the manual specifies a maximum load of 297 lbs (135 kg). Testing shows the product can handle up to 744 lbs (337.5 kg) of instantaneous load, meeting a 2.5x safety factor. However, the pull up bar's capacity also depends on the usage environment. Users should strictly adhere to the 135 kg limit

Over 250kg/550lb Capacity: This pull-up bar supports up to 550lb/250kg, ideal for larger users. Its durable design features a 2mm outer and 1.5mm inner steel pipe, ensuring long-lasting strength without deformation or breakage

No Drilling, No Traces: Utilizing innovative fixative technology, this push-up bar installs without drilling. It features 2 enlarged 9"x2" PVC mats for added grip and a fall-proof design, ensuring stability as the load increases

Double Safety Lock System: Equipped with a 360° rotatable dual gear lock, Sportneer pull up bar for doorway prevents loosening during use. It’s been rigorously tested for safety, allowing users to exercise with confidence in its sturdiness

Easy-peasy Installation: Installation is simple with detailed instructions and a video guide. Just extend to your desired height and length. Ensure your wall or doorway is sturdy; avoid ceramic tiles or glass for best results

Integrated, Extensible Structure: Unlike typical foam bars, this pull-up bar features an integrated, anti-slip cotton handle for a flexible grip. It adjusts from 30" to 37.4" (76cm to 95cm), perfect for various workouts like pull-ups and strength training

title: Pull-Up Push-Up Chin-Up Dip & Core Workout Bar • Strength Training Upper Body Multi-Purpose Workout & Exercise Bar • Fits Standard Interior Doorways 24"-32" Wide
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
description: Become the best version of yourself! Develop great upper body strength including; your core, chest, shoulders, arms, and back. With this easy to install door frame bar - you get it all. Perform a variety of exercises and different types of pull-ups with the comfort grips from nearly any interior doorway (ranging from 24" - 32" wide). There are several grip options - standard grip overhand pull-ups, wide-grip pull-ups, neutral-grip pull-ups, or opposite grip (one overhand - the other underhand) pull-ups, there are plenty of ways to challenge yourself and mix things up in your pull-up routine all while strengthening your back, shoulders and arms. The challenge continues when you take your workout bar to the floor. Not only do you have multiple options with pull-ups, you also have a wide array of choices to select when doing floor exercises as well. Try mixing up your hand positions when doing push-ups with wide, narrow, and neutral grips. Each of these will develop different areas of your chest, shoulders, and arms. Turn your body over and grab the curved handles to perform some dips and work on the triceps. You can also add to the intensity by putting some weight onto your lap...but wait, there's more! Put the bar back in the door frame at the floor level and use it as a holder for your feet to get some hardcore core and ab work done. Mix in different variations of ab exercises to really get that hard earned six pack you've been looking for. Put the bar back up in the top of the door frame to get some hanging leg raises in. Turn yourself into the man you know you can be with the help of the pull-up and push-up workout bar!
features: ★ MULTI-PURPOSE WORKOUT BAR: The variations of exercises to turn your upper body into a strong, well developed, muscular machine are wide ranging. From pull-ups to push-ups to dips to core with multiple grip options - allows you to work on becoming the envy of your neighborhood

★ SIMPLE ASSEMBLY & INSTALLS IN THE DOOR IN SECONDS: Easy instructions and hardware are included. Once you assemble the bar, simply put it in any standard interior doorway (from 24"-32" wide), use the leverage from the doorway to get to work on your body right away (holds up to 250 lbs)

★ FROM BEGINNER TO MASTER: Whether you are just starting out or can knock out 100 pull-ups in 30 minutes - use the bar to develop your skill no matter where you currently are on the spectrum. Beginners can use the ground, a chair, or a stool to assist them as they build strength to complete their first pull-up. For those who are more advanced, mix up hand positions and try different grips to keep things interesting

★ GET RESULTS BY CHANGING THINGS UP: For best results, don't exercise the same muscle groups everyday - mix things up. aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer

The Joist Mount Pull Up Bar is built heavy for intense workouts 
Better Workouts Every Day 
Made with thick wall steel and bolted to the structure of your home, the Joist Mounted Pull Up Bar is the rock solid alternative to a doorway pull up bar for pullups. Overhead mounting provides placement flexibility so you can maximize floor space beneath the bar. Premium high density foam pads over knurled steel grips offer comfort options to support your best stamina over longer workouts. Quality construction lets you focus on form and repetition. 
Ultra-stable upgrade from a doorway pull up bar 
Ideal anchor for optional accessories like Ab Straps and Bodyweight Resistance Trainers (sold separately) 
Four grip positions for better targeting and variation 
Joist Mount Pull Up Bar and Option Packages 
The premium pull up bar that bolts to any beam in your home 
Rapidly develop shoulder, arm and back strength with the Joist Mount Pull Up Bar by Ultimate Body Press. Easily mounted to any exposed beam in your home, the Joist Mount Pull Up Bar targets distinct muscle groups with four grip positions including ideal 21” spacing on the parallel grips. Expand to your results with optional Ab Strap and Bodyweight Resistance Trainers packages. (sold separately) 
Heavy-duty joist mounted pull up bar with parallel grips 
Four pull up grip positions: Parallel | Narrow | Standard | Wide 
14” tall risers, 21” parallel grip spacing, 42” wide bar 
Includes mounting hardware, complete instructions and template 
Includes through bolts and lag bolts for compatibility with thicker beams. 
Ab Straps Get the Core Results You Want (sold separately) 
Ultimate Body Press Ab Straps make it easy to activate your core, burn fat, and build muscle fast with hanging knee raises - the best exercise there is for your abs. The key to Ultimate Body Press Abs straps are the comfortable and strong sectional foam padding and adjustable loop size. With your weight comfortably off your wrists, you can readily complete full sets of hanging knee raises with good form. The results are fast and it's easy to love how hanging knee raises make you look and move. 
Ab Straps also let you spend more time engaging large muscle groups for maximum metabolic activation. Ab straps do reduce your bodyweight but your entire upper body is active during the set - from your hands and wrists, through you arms and shoulders, chest, and back. And Ab Straps give you a fantastic leverage point to turn on your lats. 
Upgrade your pull up bar and get more out of your workouts with Ab Straps by Ultimate Body Press. (package sold separately)

description: The Firstlaw Fitness I-Beam Pull Up Bar is the only one that uses 1-1/4" diameter steel tubing. This makes it the strongest one on the market. Don't be fooled by other I-Beam Pull Up Bars that claim to use 1-1/4" steel tubing but ship 1.0" steel tubing. We are proud to supply the United States Navy with our I-Beam Pull Up Bars (see product images). The United States Military has strict guidelines for strength and durability, which our product had no trouble meeting. The I-Beam Pull Up Bar is easy to install in 15 minutes or less, no drilling required. The unique design uses (6) bolts to clamp to the bottom flange of the I-Beam. Once installed it feels like the Pull Up Bar is welded to the I-Beam. It comes with foam rubber grips that give you 3 different pull up variations (wide, close, and pistol grip). These different variations isolate different muscles giving you a more complete workout. The Firstlaw Fitness I-Beam Pull Up Bar is engineered to last. It comes with a LIFETIME WARRANTY and is 100% made in the USA. If you have access to a steel I-beam you have to try the Firstlaw Fitness I-Beam Pull Up Bar. If you are not 100% satisfied with this product return it for a full refund, no questions asked. Please contact Firstlaw Fitness with any questions through Amazon or direct from our website.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
LADER —— Pull Up Bar for Doorway 
Why Do We Need a Pull Up Bar At Home? 
For better workouts every day! 
You can create your own indoor gym this winter! 
If you want to improve your fitness, this is a good choice for you! 
This pull up bar exists to inspire active, healthy lifestyles with products that make fitness attainable and enjoyable for everyone! 
Private Home Gym 
ou can create your own indoor gym this winter!Pull-up bars are perfect for pull-ups, chin-ups, sit-ups, dips, crunches, triceps dips, leg raises and more. Easy to carry it and hassle-free to install. No need go to gym to waste your time, just start your workout at home or office any time! 
Specifications 
Material: Steel Tube, EVA Foam, Rubber
Max Load: 550 lbs (250kg)
Bar Length: 29.9''~37.4''(76cm-95cm)
Advanced Structure: No screw & No trace
Safety Tips: 
Do not jump up to grab the pull up bar. 
Minors should use the bar under the supervision of a guardian. 
It is forbidden to use the doorway pull up bar to stand upside down and other dangerous actions. 
Details 
Unique Bubble Level Meter 
LADER pull up bar is equipped with Bubble Level Meter, It will help you install better. 
NEW Anti-Skid Device 
nti-skid device on both sides, which can firmly stick on the wall.when pull the bar,It will spread the gravity to both sides.So have higher slip resistance ,ensures stability. 
Prevent from sliding 
Safety buckle device, Lock the pull up bar according to the prompt direction, rotate to tight, make exercise more secure. 
Comfortable Grips 
Comfort Grips Minimize risks of calluses or hand cramping with padded handles.Deodorant, sweat absorbing, tear resistant, and can prevent the rod metal from being corroded by sweat. 
Multi-Purpose Home Pull Up Bar 
Sit-up 
It can exercise the muscles of the waist and abdomen. 
Push-up 
It can exercise the muscles of the pectoral, waist and abdomen. 
Stretching exercise 
It can exercise your body flexibility and warm-up exercises before exercise. 
Pull-up 
It can exercise the upper body muscles, mainly training latissimus dorsi.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
POWER TOWERS from K Kingkang 
The Power Tower is a versatile piece of equipment that offers numerous benefits if used properly. 
Full Body Workouts: We will give you an example full body workout that can be done while only using your body and the Power Tower. The only muscle groups that are difficult to work hard on the Power Tower are legs because you’re suspended in air for the most part. You can perform multiple compound exercises like pull-ups, dips and push-ups on the Power Tower to help stimulate muscle growth. Performing bodyweight exercises will help you to maintain and improve your overall health. The Power Tower allows users to make most exercises either easier or more difficult by incorporating supplemental tools like resistance bands, weights, weighted vests, suspension trainers and more. 
Unique Bend Suction Cups 
This dip stands owns a unique Bend suction cups in the bottom, which can adjust the flatness that contacts with the ground. Made the power tower more Safety and strong stability. 
Pull-up Benefits 
Pull ups are an excellent exercise to get stronger. They work multiple muscle groups simultaneously, which is why they help you build more strength and muscle than other exercises. 
Vertical Knee Raises 
Vertical knee raises are one way to increase core strength, and a strong core helps with everyday movement both inside and outside the gym, from getting out of bed in the morning to lifting a barbell, A strong core also helps with form, increases athleticism, improves posture, protects organs, and reduces your risk of injury. 
Push-up bar benefits 
It's easy to think that push-ups are only good for your chest and arms. But compound exercise engages multiple muscle groups at once. push-ups work your: 
Chest (pectorals) 
Shoulders (deltoids) 
Arms (triceps and biceps) 
Back (latissimus dorsi and erector spinae) 
Stomach (abdominals) 
Hips (gluteals) 
Long-size Base Support 
49.2” Long-size base has more loading points, which makes the power tower more stable 
Comfortable & Durable Leather Pads 
High quality arm and back cushions made of breathable odorless PU Leather, which give users a fully concentrated, comfortable workout without worrying about any unnecessary strain during exercise. 
Adjustable Height Power tower 
The height of this power tower can be adjusted, there are 7 holes location, the adjustable height range is 64.9-88.6 inches. 
Power tower detail size 
The most suitable size, suitable for most people

features: UPGRATED WIDETH ADJUSTABLE DOORWAY PULL UP BAR: Real adjustable width design can match your doorway more accurately, even doors in the corner. This door frame pull-up bar has a width of 5 gears and can be precisely mounted on any standard 21.65 "- 39.37" wide doorways,depth of 4.7"-8.27",Acceptable trim height up to 3.75"，easy to install and remove.

HEAVY DUTY CONSTRUCTION，HOLD UP TO 500 LBS: The pull-up bar make of 1.7mm thickened refined heavy steel.Original no break in the middle , double steel pipe superposition design make it can hold up to 500 lbs.We use high quality lock nuts make sure the home pull up bar never gets loose.The fine powder coating prevent rust and corrosion.And the handles are coated with high fiber foam,comfortable grip, multi-function, anti-slip and wear resistance.

UPGRADED SILICONE PROTECTION FOR DOOR FRAME:Doorframe pullup bar uses leverage to hold against the doorway so there are no screws.And we have upgraded the traditional foam that contacts the door frame to elastic silicone material.Permanent use,better fits and protects door frame without marks,and no damage to door.

MULTI-FUNCTION HOME GYM:Target multiple upper body & core muscles with pull-ups, push-ups, dips, and hanging crunches, multiple functions replace all other equipment.With this pull up bar, home and office become your gym and you can do exercises in a quick way.

SECURE & SAFE & 180-Days Free Return : Simple and easy to install or uninstall and store when there is limited space. aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Ally Peaks 5+2 Multiple Levels Width Adjustable Pull Up Bar Accurately Match Your Wide and Narrow doorframe 
Experience The Difference 
OUR DUTY:Provide more perfect products for your more perfect life. 
Let us start your training with Ally Pesaks. 
Everytime we try our best to make our product better.And we insist on using the best materials for our products.Because we hope you will be happy when you receive our products and it is helpful for you.Our greatest wish is that you will feel secure and happy when you use our products.AND OUR DISTINGUISHED CUSTOMER ARE WORTH IT. 
WHY CHOOSE OUR 5+2 PULL UP BAR - SIX CHARACTERISTICS OF OUR PULL UP BAR 
Original (5+2) level width adjustable structure 
This pull up bar have 5 levels width and2 levels thickness for adjustment， So that it can be precisely mounted on any standard 21.65 "- 39.37" wide doorways,depth of 4.7"-8.27" 
(Please note:This 5+2 structure not only a boon for narrow and wide door frames, but also provides a stronger structure for standard door frames.) 
Upgraded double silicone protection for door frame 1/2 
All customers who have purchased the same type of doorway pull-up bar will find that the foam(between the door frame and the bar) is damaged after a short time of use without exception, then damage the door frame. It causes great annoyance to users. 
In order to completely eliminate this situation, we creatively upgraded our pull up bar to a full circle of ultra-thick elastic silicone protective covers. It can perfectly match and protect the door frame while being used permanently. 
Upgraded double silicone protection for door frame 2/2 
The chin up bar comes with a pair of extra 4mm No-Trace removable silicone pads.Why are we still equipped with extra silicone pads for this pull up bar?Because we find that when we do exercise there is not only an inward force on the door frame but also an upward and downward force of friction.So double silicone protection(double insurance) is the best way to permanently prevent the bar damage to door frame. 
THICKENED STEEL PIPE SUPER HEAVY DUTY 
The doorway pull up bar is made of 1.7MM Thickened steel .Matching the double stacking structure allows the pullup bar to support up to 500LBS. 
HIGH QUALITY LOCK NUTS 
High quality Stainless Self-Locking Nylon Insert make sure the bar never gets loose.BE MORE SECURE 
All parts of pull up bar are made of thickened refined heavy steel+Grade A High-density foams .In order to cut cost,some ordinary doorway pull up bar’s some part are made of hollow plastic,this part will not strong enough. 
Pull up bar with three grip positions, narrow, wide, and neutral.Target multiple upper body & core muscles with pull-ups, push-ups, dips, and sit-ups.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Why Do You Need a Pull Up Bar? 
Doing chin-ups and using our pull-up bar can develop and tone muscles such as pectoralis major, latissimus dorsi, and biceps brachii. 
The pull-up bar has versatile uses such as pull-ups, chin-ups, push-ups, dips, and sit-ups. You can also use the pull-up bar to hang a yoga trapeze or swing.
This dip bar is a convenient addition to a home gym and allows you to exercise at home or in the office. If you want to improve your health and fitness, HANDSONIC’s pull-up bar is an excellent choice for you.
The pull-up bar is cost-effective. Save on a costly gym memberships by using our pull-up bar. If you have a door frame, you’re ready to do pull-ups!

Handsonic is the provider of sports products 
Missions: Continuous innovation of technology is an eternal target of our enterprise. 
Values: We strictly control the quality of our products and provide excellent services for our customers. 
Advanced Equipment 
Strict QC Procedures 
Credible Quality 
Sincere Service 
Handsonic 2021 New Design Non-Slip Pull Up Bar 
You get fit by playing the game, day in, day out, morning, noon, and night. 
Retractable to accommodate different widths
Household use and effortless installation
No drilling required
Easy to install and store
High-quality steel bearing up to 440 Lbs 
Suitable for wall or door frame of 28.7”-36.2.”
Before installing the pull-up bar, please confirm whether the door frame is solid. 
Before using the pull-up bar, be sure to note the different distances corresponding to the areas of installation. 
Please select the appropriate installation distance and pull-up bar specifications. The pull-up bar can not exceed the maximum installation distance. 
Do not mount on hollow glass or unstable objects. 
Do not use beyond the load-bearing range. 
Security Update 
With a high-density thread retractable rod, the retractable range is smaller, the wall is more compact and can be lengthened to 36.2”/92cm.
Stainless steel horn buckle is a two-way 360° locked horn preventing slipping, increasing the security of the pull-up bar.
High Quality Material 
The pull up bar is made of the highest quality materials and integrates the best in technology. 
Professional quality materials coupled with refined workmanship, produced exquisite and durable chin up bar.
Non-Skid&Demountable Holder 
Absorbent and skid proof cotton pad is easy to disassemble and clean, easy to clean. 
Locking Principle 
The heavier the bearing, squeezes to the middle and both sides, and the tighter the steel pipe is, the safer it is.
Installation Steps 
STEP 1 
Pull the anti-locking locks at both ends of the bar first.
STEP 2 
Rotate the two ends and adjust the length to the size of the installation position. The bar should be stuck in the installation position. Then finely adjust the pull-up bar to the horizontal position.

Handsonic 2021 New Design Non-Slip Pull Up Bar 
You get fit by playing the game, day in, day out, morning, noon, and night. 
Retractable to accommodate different widths
Household use and effortless installation
No drilling required
Easy to install and store
High-quality steel bearing up to 440 Lbs

Before installing the pull-up bar, please confirm whether the door frame is solid. 
Before using the pull-up bar, be sure to note the different distances corresponding to the areas of installation. 
Please select the appropriate installation distance and pull-up bar specifications. The pull-up bar can not exceed the maximum installation distance. 
Do not mount on hollow glass or unstable objects. 
Do not use beyond the load-bearing range. 
Security Update 
With a high-density thread retractable rod, the retractable range is smaller, the wall is more compact and can be lengthened to 36.2”/92cm.
Stainless steel horn buckle is a two-way 360° locked horn preventing slipping, increasing the security of the pull-up bar.
High Quality Material 
The pull up bar is made of the highest quality materials and integrates the best in technology. 
Professional quality materials coupled with refined workmanship, produced exquisite and durable chin up bar.
Non-Skid&Demountable Holder 
Absorbent and skid proof cotton pad is easy to disassemble and clean, easy to clean. 
Locking Principle 
The heavier the bearing, squeezes to the middle and both sides, and the tighter the steel pipe is, the safer it is.
Installation Steps 
STEP 1 
Pull the anti-locking locks at both ends of the bar first.
STEP 2 
Rotate the two ends and adjust the length to the size of the installation position. The bar should be stuck in the installation position. Then finely adjust the pull-up bar to the horizontal position.
STEP 3 
After adjusting the position of the pull-up bar, hold the middle tube with both hands and continue to rotate in the direction of extension until it stops. Put the anti-lock sleeve into the card slot, and pull down the wrench to lock the pipe.
After completion, pull the pull up bar hard and pull the body down to check whether the installation is firm. The pull-up bar can be used once after it secured.

The heavier the bearing, squeezes to the middle and both sides, and the tighter the steel pipe is, the safer it is.

After completion, pull the pull up bar hard and pull the body down to check whether the installation is firm. The pull-up bar can be used once after it secured.

title: JFIT Deluxe Multi Exercise Doorway Pull-Up Bar with Comfort Grips, 40-Inch
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
description: LONGEST LENGTH BAR AVAILABLE Made in Taiwan with high grade materials, this Pull-Up bar fits doorway openings up to 40” long. With a minimum length measuring 25.25” this bar can hold up to 300lbs. Only a screwdriver or drill needed for installing, this premium pull-up bar comes with the mounting bracket, screws, and sit-up plugs needed for safety. For safety and stability, screws are provided and required for mounting. Quality adjustable hand grips made with neoprene material and Velcro allowing these removable hand grips to be placed where they are comfortable for you. Not just for Chin-Ups and Pull-Ups, mount to the bottom of a doorway to maximize your sit-ups, crunches and even triceps dips, making it easy to move locations with extra door mounts available. For safety purposes, the bar extrudes from one telescopic point, as tighter threads and toggle ends make sure that bar is safely tight and secure. End caps for ultimate safety and rubber stoppers for metal doors.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Features 
Bar Extends from One End Only 
Simply twist to extend bar. Unlike bars that extend from both sides, the j/fit bar extends from one end only to create a stronger safer bar. 
Won't Ruin Your Woodwork 
Small screws can be placed in even the nicest of woodwork. When ready to remove, simply putty, smooth and apply light paint. This method saves doorway woodwork more so than not as using safety end caps will not let the bar indent or mark the wood. 
Complete Set with Everything You Need to Get Started 
The doorway gym bar comes with a set of safety brackets, a set of sit up plugs and adjustable comfort grips. Extra end caps and grips are available through purchase. 
Great for Sit Ups and Push Ups 
Install the red sit up dots to the bottom of your doorway and use the bar control your sit ups. Add a medicine ball for added resistance. 
Use for Dips 
Place the red dots anywhere on the door to give you your desired height to perform dips working out all areas of the arms and upper back. 
Perform the Perfect Push Up 
Relieve stress on your wrists while doing push ups. Place the bar at a height that allows you to get a deeper push up. Adjust the grips to position your hands to work out different muscle groups. 
Great for Gymnastic workouts 
Small red rubber dots are included to allow set up to perform sit ups, push ups and dips. One bar, many uses. Easy to move from top of doorway for pull ups and chin ups to lower door for sit ups, push ups, dips and more. 
Sit ups 
Tricep dips 
Push ups 
Gymnastic workouts 

Fits in most doorways from 31" to 40". 
Located in Montana 
Customer support team that answers the phone and your questions. 
Easy to Install 
You Only Need A Screwdriver 
Install in minutes. The safety end caps keep your door from being damaged or marked up and keeps you safe. Please check doorway bar before each use to make sure it is tightly installed. 
Easy to take down when not in use 
Easy to move from top of doorway to bottom 
Place it at proper height for your needs

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Features 
Bar Extends from One End Only 
Simply twist to extend bar. Unlike bars that extend from both sides, the j/fit bar extends from one end only to create a stronger safer bar. 
Won't Ruin Your Woodwork 
Small screws can be placed in even the nicest of woodwork. When ready to remove, simply putty, smooth and apply light paint. This method saves doorway woodwork more so than not as using safety end caps will not let the bar indent or mark the wood. 
Complete Set with Everything You Need to Get Started 
The doorway gym bar comes with a set of safety brackets, a set of sit up plugs and adjustable comfort grips. Extra end caps and grips are available through purchase. 
Great for Sit Ups and Push Ups 
Install the red sit up dots to the bottom of your doorway and use the bar control your sit ups. Add a medicine ball for added resistance. 
Use for Dips 
Place the red dots anywhere on the door to give you your desired height to perform dips working out all areas of the arms and upper back. 
Perform the Perfect Push Up 
Relieve stress on your wrists while doing push ups. Place the bar at a height that allows you to get a deeper push up. Adjust the grips to position your hands to work out different muscle groups. 
Great for Gymnastic workouts 
Small red rubber dots are included to allow set up to perform sit ups, push ups and dips. One bar, many uses. Easy to move from top of doorway for pull ups and chin ups to lower door for sit ups, push ups, dips and more.

Great for toning abs and obliques. 
Made to professional standard, with Safety Lock snap hooks Isolates abs for total ab development. 
MADE FOR RESULTS 
For sure you will be satisfied from the purchase and you will find many different ways to use them.

You two together will be unstoppable and within time you will surely get that wanted 6 pack! Get all the benefits from the abs straps, like stronger core and a 6 pack, don’t wait anymore! 
PREMIUM QUALITY THAT YOU DESERVE 
Our Ab Straps are not cheap regular Ab Slings. You will get very special Abdominal Core Trainer. 
With the great up to date design we added extra padding for the elbows which gives you the good feeling named “comfort”. 
So with this privilege you can do more reps and therefore you can pump more blood to your core and make it fit and strong. 
DESIGNED TO MAKE YOU FIT! 
With the big and strong clips you can go and use them everywhere you go. You just need a pull-up bar or something similar to hang from and you can go ahead and do some leg raises to get those abs you want so much! 
Also our Premium Handing Ab Straps improves your stability! 
Made to professional standard, with Safety Lock snap hooks Isolates abs for total ab development. 
SAFE AND SECURE 
Thanks to the high quality of the materials, you can be 100% sure that you are hanging safe during the exercise and there is no chance of falling or breaking the heavy duty steel clips. 
The Hanging Abs can handle weights up to 400 pounds and the steel clips can go up to 10 000 pounds. 
ARMAGEDDON SPORTS got you covered! 
REASONS TO TRY THEM 
You came here because you need something to boost your workout and to build some core strength, right? Well, the good news are that you are on the right place and here is why our ab slings are perfect for you: 
- Fits all bar sizes; 
- Maximum efficiency; 
- Large padded arm support; 
- Sturdy and durable gym equipment; 
- To protect your arms, palms and elbows; 
- If you are stuck and to get the six-pack you want; 
Time is the most valuable thing – DON’T waste it! 
You Need Superb Quality Ab Straps For Safety Abdominal Training 
COMFORT BEYOND YOUR IMAGINATIONS! 
The ergonomic design fits you perfect no matter your body type. Enjoy with ease these abdominal crunch straps and forget about rubbed skin. There is no need to have a strong grip to hold on your weight, you just need the ab straps for full upper body workout. Now you can get the results you have always wanted and build a strong core and great abs! Increase your power, the blood flow around your belly, and burn calories. 
HUGE D-RINGS FITS ON ALL BARS! 
Do you want to lose weight? You are stuck and your abs don’t want to show up? Why don’t you try the abdominal sling straps and make sure that they work exactly as you want! Use them whenever you see a bar and easily attach them to it. Mostly used at the gym, at home or at the park, also in sports like calisthenics, crossfit, and weightlifting. It’s the equipment that will help you waste no more time and get the abs you deserve. 
ATTRACTIVE DESIGN AND EXTRA DURABLE! 
Our strong team of designers made them perfect from start to the end and they will look amazing on you! Also, they are used to remove the stress on shoulders and increase the stability in arms. Nylon straps are extremely strong and no matter what you do, there is no chance of breaking them. We use only high-quality materials and they will never break or rip apart like the cheap ones.

title: Sportsroyals Pull up Bar Multi-Function Power Tower Dip Station Core Training Fitness Equipment 400LBS
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Dip Stands
features: 【Solid Safety】The "Π"-shaped base design maximizes the support area, and anti-sway reinforced shock-absorbing pads are added to the support points to enhance the stability of the machine. Designed for high-intensity training, it's made from commercial-grade steel and is durable enough to hold up to 400 pounds, while non-slip padding and wider support keep you safe during high-intensity workouts.

【Ultimate Strength Trainer】Sportsroyals Multi-Purpose Power Tower has a variety of training methods to activate muscle fibres in all directions, pull-ups are a golden move to build your back, and consistent pull-up training improves cardiorespiratory endurance and helps to improve cardiovascular health.

【9-level Height for Family】There are 9 height adjustments for pull-ups, from 57.09"-86.61". There is a height adjustment knob that can be easily adjusted. It is suitable for both teenagers and adults to exercise.

【Soft Foam Covered for Better Grip】The pull-up bar is covered with soft foam for a comfortable experience. Whether held with a wide or narrow grip, it helps you build all-round back muscles and upper body strength. The length of the pull-up bar is 41 inches, providing plenty of room for pull-ups.

【Effortless Installation】The included accessories include installation tools. Follow the clear instructions in the instructions. Install the base in the first step, install the pull-up bar in the second step, and install the back cushion and armrest pad in the third step. It is easy to assemble in three steps.

【Give You a Better Sports Experience】In order to make the back and arms fit more closely with the cushion and the posture to be more natural during exercise, the specially designed widened and thickened cushion (5 adjustment holes) and the elbow cushion with an inclination of 10 degrees are more ergonomic. Make training more scientific and safer.

【Only 9.8 sq ft Footprint】For users with limited living space, the home pull-up is an ideal fitness tool. It takes up about 9.8 square inches and is fairly easy to store. It is also very convenient when you want to exercise.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Stamina X | Boulder Doorway Trainer 
The Stamina X Boulder Doorway Trainer is the ultimate training tool to strengthen and develop your shoulders, back, and arms. 
Added challenge to build grip and forearm strength 
The unique rock climbing grips provide an advanced challenge when you're ready to take your workout to the next level. 
Because it fits in any standard doorframe with sturdy trim, the Boulder Doorway Trainer is portable and easy to assemble. 
Go from the Ground Up 
The Boulder Doorway Trainer is perfect for traditional pull-ups and chin-ups as it fits in your door frame. It also doubles as a ground trainer, making it ideal for performing sit-ups, push-ups and tricep dips. Multiple grip positions allow you to target different muscle groups quickly and easily. 
The simple assembly, portability and removability of the trainer makes it ideal for anyone with space constraints because you don’t have to have any hardware to remove it from the doorframe. As long as you have a standard doorframe*, you can harness the power of the Stamina X Boulder Fit Doorway Trainer. 
*Requires sturdy doorway with trim. 
Supported by müüv 
Experience connected fitness with this home gym equipment with the müüv app. With smart guided coaching, exercise demo videos, personalized workouts, assembly videos, and more, müüv provides the best workout and fitness experience with your Stamina equipment. Download the müüv app on the Apple App Store or the Google Play store.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Stamina X | Boulder Doorway Trainer 
The Stamina X Boulder Doorway Trainer is the ultimate training tool to strengthen and develop your shoulders, back, and arms. 
Added challenge to build grip and forearm strength 
The unique rock climbing grips provide an advanced challenge when you're ready to take your workout to the next level. 
Because it fits in any standard doorframe with sturdy trim, the Boulder Doorway Trainer is portable and easy to assemble. 
Go from the Ground Up 
The Boulder Doorway Trainer is perfect for traditional pull-ups and chin-ups as it fits in your door frame. It also doubles as a ground trainer, making it ideal for performing sit-ups, push-ups and tricep dips. Multiple grip positions allow you to target different muscle groups quickly and easily. 
The simple assembly, portability and removability of the trainer makes it ideal for anyone with space constraints because you don’t have to have any hardware to remove it from the doorframe. As long as you have a standard doorframe*, you can harness the power of the Stamina X Boulder Fit Doorway Trainer. 
*Requires sturdy doorway with trim. 
Supported by müüv 
Experience connected fitness with this home gym equipment with the müüv app. With smart guided coaching, exercise demo videos, personalized workouts, assembly videos, and more, müüv provides the best workout and fitness experience with your Stamina equipment. Download the müüv app on the Apple App Store or the Google Play store.

title: Pull Up Bar for Doorway: Sportneer Strength Training Pull-up Bars without Screw - Adjustable Width Locking Mechanism Chin Up Bar, Thickened Steel Max Limit 440 lbs Upper Body Fitness Pullup Bars for Home (Black-Red)
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
features: Before purchasing, please make sure that the size of your door frame is 29.5 in-37 in (75 cm-94 cm). This Chin up Bar is not suitable for door frame widths outside this range; The width of the door frame must be wider than the width of the anti-slip pads at both ends of the pull up bar

To ensure safety, the manual specifies a maximum load of 297 lbs (135 kg). Testing shows the product can handle up to 744 lbs (337.5 kg) of instantaneous load, meeting a 2.5x safety factor. However, the pull up bar's capacity also depends on the usage environment. Users should strictly adhere to the 135 kg limit

No Drilling, No Traces: The pull-up bar uses innovative fixative technology to stay in place. It features two large 6.5 x 1.8-inch PVC mats for added friction and stability. Four metal fixed points connect the base and bar, ensuring a secure, fall-proof design even under heavy loads

Heavy Duty Construction: Our Pull Up Bar supports up to 440 lbs (200 kg) with its 2 mm outer and 1.5 mm inner steel pipes. This pull-up bar built to last without deforming or breaking, ensuring durability for your home gym. Note: Longer use distances may reduce the load of chin-up bar

Upgraded Mechanic Lock System: This push-up bar features a new 360-degree rotatable dual gear lock on both ends to protect the bar from loosening. The doorway exercise bar has passed extensive testing, ensuring safety and sturdiness for confident use

Easy Installation: Install quickly with detailed instructions, a video guide, and arrow markers on the chin-up bar. Spirit levels on both ends ensure correct setup. Ensure your doorway or wall is solid; avoid ceramic tiles, glass or non-solid doorframe. Note: Verify the marked rotation direction; reversing it may cause locking

Integrated, Extensible Structure: Unlike most 2-section foam bars, this doorway pull up bar features an ultra long, integrated anti-slip cotton handlebar for a flexible grip. It's sweat-resistant, odorless, and durable. Twist the bar to adjust its length from 29.5 to 37 inches (75 to 94 cm) for various workouts like pull-ups, sit-ups, push-ups, stretching and more

title: Sunny Health & Fitness Doorway Chin Up Pull Up Bar
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
description: Maximize your workout with the Sunny Health & Fitness Doorway Chin-Up Bar. Sturdy, chrome plated steel bar, with a max weight capacity of 220 lb. , and non-slip, soft padded hand grips ensure maximum stability and grip. The simplicity of the Sunny Health & Fitness Doorway Chin Up Bar is its strongest asset as it allows you to have full control of your workout. Adjustable length (24. 5 to 36 inches) provides a customizable workout area and fits into any standard door frame. It is the ultimate multi-tool workout bar as it is ideal for pull-ups, chin-ups, leg lifts, or you can use it as a foot anchor for sit-ups and crunches. Includes weight bearing brackets for maximum stability during your chin-ups and non-weight bearing brackets for sit-ups; the brackets ensure you are adequately supported during your exercise.
features: STURDY CHROME PLATED STEEL BAR: Train like a pro with the tough and secure exercise trainer supporting tough workouts. When mounted properly, the fitness bar holds up to 220 pounds giving you full support for pull-up and chin ups.
ADJUSTABLE LENGTH: Easily adjust this exercise bar so you can take your fitness on the go! Adjustable length (24. 5 to 36 inches) provides a customizable workout.

COMFORT GRIPS: Minimize risks of calluses or hand cramping with padded handles. Non-slip extra-long foam grips for extra comfort to minimize hand fatigue. Put the door bar lower to the ground and use it to help you perform push-ups!
MAXIMUM STABILITY: Includes weight bearing brackets for maximum stability during your chin-ups and non-weight bearing brackets for sit-ups. Fits into any standard door frame
EASY STORAGE: Set up in seconds in almost any doorframe and easily store away in a closet. Adjustable length (24. 5 to 36 inches) provides a customizable workout for your home and body.

Let us start your training with Ally Pesaks. 
Everytime we try our best to make our product better.And we insist on using the best materials for our products.Because we hope you will be happy when you receive our products and it is helpful for you.Our greatest wish is that you will feel secure and happy when you use our products.AND OUR DISTINGUISHED CUSTOMER ARE WORTH IT.

modules.title: MULTI-FUNCTION HOME GYM
modules.subtitle: THICKENED SSTEEL PULL UP BAR  SUPPORT UP TO 440LBS

centerColumn.text: Begin to plan your home workout and unlock their full with Ally Peaks pull up bar.Let every door be your personal gym.The doorway pull up bar with three grip positions, narrow, wide, and neutral.Target multiple upper body & core muscles with pull-ups, push-ups, dips, and sit-ups.With this pull up bar, home and office become your gym.High fiber material foams on the grips let your workout more comfortable.Powerful double protection system for the door frame make your workout more secure.
centerColumn.textBox:
The door pull up bar can be used on 24 "to 32" width and 4.7 "to 7.5"depth door frame.PLEASE CHECK YOUR DOOR FRAME BEFORE ORDERING 
Please stick the protection pads on the door frame where the frame and the bar are in contact to protect your door frame

rightColumn.title: SUPPLEMENTARY TRAINING
rightColumn.text: You can use the resistance bands as your supplementary training.When you do not have enough strength after you do some training,you can continue training with those resistance bands.The fitness effect will be more obvious both of them are used together.
rightColumn.textBox:
Resistance bands package includes 2*resistance bands(1 for 30lb &1 for 25lb),2*handles,1*Door Anchor. 
Can do some training for back, shoulders, chest, arms, legs,triceps, biceps and so on

title: DOBESTS Foldable Power Tower Pull Up Bar Dip Station Adjustable Multifunction Workout Pull Up Tower Station Gym Strength Training Equipment for Home Outdoor, Triangular Legs, Support 700lbs
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Dip Stands
features: 【Foldable Pull Up Bar Station】：This power tower pull up bar is made up of a foldable triangular structure design, more stabler than an H-shaped power tower dip station. You can easily fold up the power tower dip station after the workout, saving space, great for limited space

【8 Adjustable Heights, Whole Family Workout 】: The pull up bar station has 8-levers to adjust different height, 7-levers to adjust the handle height,both the front and back of power tower station can be used,suitable for whole family different heights workout for home or outdoor training.

【Fairly Stable and Safer 】: The triangular construction provides the pull-up station with strong stability. We also added 4 anti-slip rubber on the bottom foot tube,and 8 safety pins to keep everything in place and prevent it from collapsing, making the standing pull-up bar tower fairly sturdy, no wobble, safe enough for various exercises.

【No Shoulders Limited or Hitting Legs and Shins On】: The pull up bar stand is designed with a width of 36.2 inches, which provides spacious space for shoulders， especially friendly for wide shoulders. Easily doing a pull-up, elbow bend, and knee raise, and no worry about hitting legs and shins.

【Multifunctional Power Tower Pull Up Station For Home/Outdoor】This is a power tower workout station that supports full body workout: vertical knee lifting, arms support, pull up, dips, push up, and inverted rows, effectively exercising your abdominal muscles, arms, back, leg, shoulders strength, great workout stations for home gym

【Loading Capacity up to 700 pounds】: The chin up bar dip station is made up of 2mm thickened material, 40mm-50mm thickening steel pipe, very durable to support weight up tp 700 lbs, it will not easily bend or deform

features: 【Sturdy and Durable】: Trlakepreble is constructed from high-quality steel to guarantee its sturdiness and durability. The well-designed structure ensures the stability of the steel frame, while the suction cups on the bottom prevent slipping and protect the floor from damage. It is capable of supporting up to 330 pounds of weight.

【Height Adjustable】:The power tower station has 6 adjustable height ranges from 65" to 83". Trlakepreble power tower is suitable for the whole family workout,A variety of height options make it ideal for exercise for the whole family.
【Versatile Design】:This power tower features vertical knee lifts, push-ups, and pull-ups, offering a variety of exercises to tone and strengthen your arms, core, shoulders, and chest.

【Compact and Lightweight】As an entry-level pull-up bar, it is both functional and compact, making it lightweight. Ideal for low ceilings, it occupies minimal space on either side. Additionally, it weighs only 30 lbs, making it perfect for women; you can easily relocate it wherever you desire.
【Quick Installation】: You can do quick installation by watching the installation video on the product page, or the included instructions, even if you are inexperienced.

【Disadvantages】: 1. The power tower is not heavy, only 30 pounds, it will move forward when pulling the resistance band, you need to add weight to the bottom in advance to increase stability. 2. The height of the pull-up bar is only 83 inches, if you are over 6 feet tall, this will affect the comfort of pull-ups.

【Customer Service】: Whether it's before or after making a purchase, if you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to us! Our customer service team is highly efficient and always eager to assist you!

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Welcome to syzythoy Brand shop. 
This wall mounted pull-up bar help you full body workout to achieve your fitness targets easily and efficiently. It is simple and efficient way to strengthen your entire body in the comfort of your own home. 
What's in the package? 
1 * wall mounted pull-up bar 
What you need to install: 
12mm drill bit for the bolts(12mm is equivalent to a 3/8 drill bit).
Please note that the included hardware for mounting is for concrete/ brick applications only. 
So you will have to buy extra hardware to hang it up on drywall. Nothing special required just lag screw(lag bolts) and wood to mount to.
Exercise your body: 
Wall Mounted Requirements: 
The product should be installed on the Concrete brick/ solid cement wall/ solid red brick wall / solid tile wall.
You'd better not install the product on hollow brick wall/ honeycomb brick wall /drywall /sandwich panel.
Extra hardware required for drywall/stud mounting. 
Please note that the included hardware for mounting is for concrete/brick applications only. So you will need to supply your own hardware to mount it.
You can pick up all the supplies at Lowe's-nothing special required just lag screw(lag bolts) and wood to mount to.
Install it with your own lag bolts directly into your studs and add a 1~x4 piece of wood when it's in the dip position.
Requires wood/plywood/board backing for drywall 
It just needed to be installed over 3/4" plywood to protect the sheetrock, and make sure you install it with 3/8 lag bolts.

title: FitBeast Pull Up Bar for Doorway, Strength Training Pullup Bar with No Screws, Chin Up Bar with Adjustable Width Locking Mechanism, Doorway Pull Up Bar Max Load 600lbs for Home Gym Upper Body Workout
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
features: 𝗛𝗜𝗚𝗛 𝗟𝗢𝗔𝗗 𝗕𝗘𝗔𝗥𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝗖𝗔𝗣𝗔𝗖𝗜𝗧𝗬 — Constructed with high-quality steel tube, the core of the bar is 1.5mm in thickness which allows it to bear a weight capacity of 800lbs. The supporting feet's bow-shaped form enables them to sustain higher weight with greater friction. Can I mount it on a concrete wall? 
Yes, in the product I received, in addition to the screws for wooden beams, there were also special expansion screws for cement wall, which I used to install my pull up bar on the cement wall. 
How far from the wall is this product? 
This product is wider from the wall than most products on the market, allowing for a better workout experience. 
Is it difficult to assemble the wall pull up bar? 
It only takes half an hour to install this pull up bar according to the instructions. 
What makes this Heavy Duty Chin Up Bar better than the others and how many workouts are there? 
It's made of heavy-duty alloy steel that can withstand 600 pounds of force and can wide, narrow, neutral, ball finger and hammer grip, and it versatile for resistance training, suspension training, and strength training. 
Can the screws bear this weight? Will it break? 
This situation has been mentioned many times in reviews of other brands. Don't worry, it's very sturdy and my 260lbs weight has no problem at all.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Want to boost your home fitness routine with gym-quality pull-ups, calisthenics, and street workouts, all while enhancing your health and sculpting your body? Looking to encourage your child's growth? Seeking a hassle-free aerial yoga setup at home without the need to drill ceilings or deal with permanent hammock setups? You've found your match with our product! 
Introducing the medium-sized model of the KT folding stand frames, KT1.1518. For those seeking taller and wider options, explore ASIN B07Y3DN2QS or ASIN: B07H25C9XR. 
More than just words, our KT folding stand frames deliver satisfaction through their unique design and exceptional quality. Ideal for the savvy shopper, these products embody versatility with their MULTIPURPOSE, PORTABLE, FOLDABLE, HEIGHT ADJUSTABLE, and STURDY nature, making them a top choice for fitness enthusiasts seeking convenience and reliability in their home workout gear 
KEY FEATURES 
1. Fold up easily and Portable 
Maximize your space and maintain a clutter-free environment with our KT training stand frame. Designed for effortless folding in just 10 seconds, it transforms into a compact, long rectangular frame for convenient storage. This feature makes it ideal for any home or office setting, ensuring you can reclaim your space immediately after your workout. 
Weighing just 37.48 lbs (17kgs), the frame is light enough to be easily moved by an average person, making it a truly 'portable' piece of equipment. So, while 'portable' might not mean taking it on your travels, it does ensure that incorporating fitness into your routine is hassle-free, making it a perfect fit for your busy lifestyle 
2. Height adjustable 
Experience effortless customization with our user-friendly, adjustable-height KT training stand. Easily modify the height by hand from 72.8'' to 92.5'' (185cm - 235cm), without the need for any tools, making it a versatile addition to any room. This range includes numerous intermediate settings, ensuring a perfect fit for every pull-up user under 5.90 ft (180cm). Ideal for aerial-yoga enthusiasts under 5.57 ft (170cm), the stand is sufficiently tall to hang a short yoga hammock. 
For those suffering from lower back pain, this feature is a game-changer. You can select the ideal height for pain-free back and spine stretching exercises. Say goodbye to bending your legs or jumping to reach the bar. Regular use of this stand for dead-hangs can bring about significant and noticeable improvements in your back health, day after day. 
3. Multipurpose 
Built for strength training and helping kids grow taller, its 92.5-inch (235cm) max height lets users under 6ft perform pull-ups without toes touching the ground. But why stop there? Unleash the full potential of this product by utilizing its robust load-bearing capacity. Attach aerial yoga hammock, exercise rings, TRX straps, or a punching bag for a diverse workout experience. Transform it into a haven of relaxation with a hammock chair, or make it a playground for kids with a swing chair or rope ladder. This product is your one-stop solution for exercise, leisure, and fun! 
I’ve seen many people invest in fitness equipment only for it to gather dust when motivation fades. With our product, you won’t face that issue. Even if you take a break from your fitness routine, you can still use it in other useful ways. This versatility ensures your purchase stays valuable long after you’ve stopped training, eliminating any worry of wasted money 
4. Stable 
For pull-up enthusiasts, the robustness of our KT folding stand frame marks a significant advancement in home and office fitness equipment. We take immense pride in declaring that our product ranks among the most solid free-standing pull-up bars available in the market. 
With an extensive background in pull-ups, Mr. Khanh Trinh has always prioritized sturdiness as a critical feature for a superior pull-up bar. His 15 years of experience and dedication have led to multiple design enhancements, effectively reducing wobble by 93%. While it may not be completely motionless, its remarkable stability has earned widespread praise from experienced users, including Mr. Khanh Trinh himself. More than just a fitness tool, it's an essential daily asset for serious fitness enthusiasts 
5. Strong and durable 
Boasting an innovative A-shaped structure with support bars integrated into each of its four legs, this stand is a testament to thoughtful design and material synergy. It's built to support users up to 220.5 lbs (100kgs) for everyday exercises, maintaining its prime condition without any signs of wear. 
Capable of withstanding up to 440.9 lbs (200kgs), our stand is resilient even under the most vigorous activities like kipping pull-ups. Its robust construction ensures it will never deform or collapse, no matter the intensity of your workout. The frame's integrity remains unaltered, preserving its original shape and offering unwavering safety to all users. With this stand, you're not just investing in a piece of equipment; you're investing in a durable partner for your fitness journey 
6. High quality 
Experience the pinnacle of quality with our KT Folding Training Stand, meticulously crafted in our Vietnamese factory. We operate on a state-of-the-art semi-automatic production line, adhering to stringent quality control measures that meet ISO 9001:2015 standards and our own rigorous criteria, akin to Japanese companies' precision. 
Our commitment to excellence goes beyond cost considerations. While manufacturing in our own facility may be more expensive than outsourcing in China, this approach empowers us with complete quality control. From selecting premium raw materials to ensuring the durability of load-bearing welds between pipes, every aspect of our product is fine-tuned for superior quality. Choose KT, where we prioritize quality over cost to deliver the best to our customers 
Usage notes 
Let's adjust the length of 02 distance-setting-bars to the maximum and mount to holes in the upper position to extend the KT frame's footprint when hanging the swing chair for kids. This helps to ensure safety and the chair will fly further, makes the kids more excited 
Likewise, widen the footprint of the KT Workout Stand as much as possible when hang punching bag or perform exercises that require safety such as swing body, kipping pull-ups... The wider the footprint, the firmer the frame. 
You can do "dead-hang" without 02 distance-setting-bars (DSB) if you want a quick stretching for back pain relief. But, please mount the DSB for safety if you do other exercises such as aerial yoga, pull ups, swing body.. or you have severe spinal problems 
Currently, Khanh Trinh Joint Stock Company (Brand KT KHANH TRINH) is holding the original design with materials and specifications are calculated carefully to ensure the best Quality. We have not yet authorized production and distribution for any other Brands/companies, so please be wary of counterfeit products from other Sellers

Expandable bar ends make the Elevated Bar a universal fit for residential doorways 24–36” wide without drilling. Hardware and tools are included.  The Results you Want The Elevated Doorway Pull Up Bar extends your range of motion and brings home the performance you expect from a mounted bar. The Elevated Doorway Bar uses the thickest steel, quality hardware and our exclusive ABS couplers that lock each crossbar at 90° to the uprights. A rigid bar puts your focus on form and repetition for the results you want in less time. Designed in the USA Ultimate Body Press is a North Carolina company committed to delivering better workouts every day. Includes Prime eligible shipping and USA customer service. Shop with Confidence The Ceiling Mount Pull Up Bar is backed by Ultimate Body Press against manufacturer's defects for 10 years.
features: INCREASE STRENGTH & MOBILITY: Doorway pull-up bar creates better workouts on the wall and floor

BENEFITS ALL FITNESS LEVELS: Great for tall users and all fitness levels, 10-inch wall clearance gives you a full range of motion with more headroom; Premium high-density foam pads reduce strain to comfortably support your stamina over longer workouts

DURABLE CONSTRUCTION: Quality steel construction lets you focus on form and repetitions without worrying about stability; Heavy-duty hardware and ABS couplers stabilize you throughout your fitness journey
UNIVERSAL FIT: Universal-fit, expandable bar fits doorways 24 to 36 inches wide with up to 3.5-inch wide molding; No permanent mounting required, allowing you to use as a brace for floor exercises
WEIGHT: Supports fitness enthusiasts up to 300 pounds; Dimensions (L x W x H): 41 x 22 x 11 inches

aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer

The Elevated Doorway Pull Up Bar extends 10 inches from the doorway and 1 inch above trim. 
Expandable bar ends fit doorway 24-36" in width

XL Elevated Doorway Pull Up Bar 
Get out of the doorway for better workouts every day 
Get better workouts every day with the elevated XL Doorway Pull Up Bar by Ultimate Body Press. With wide diameter heavy steel tubing, premium hardware, exclusive ABS bar couplers and high density foam padding, The XL Doorway Pull Up Bar combines stable workouts with incredible range of motion and fits doors up to 36" wide. Three grip positions target individual muscle groups across the chest, arms, back and core. This is the bar to have when you want workouts with the feel of a mounted bar. 
Get highly metabolic home workouts that build muscle across the chest, arms, back, and core – fast 
Workouts get effective results with pull-ups, push-ups, body weight rows, dips, and sit ups 
Premium construction with quality hardware and ABS tubing couplers means true stability on the wall and real rigidity for floor exercises 
Quickly switch between doorway and floor exercises. 
High density foam grips are long lasting and reduce strain for better workouts 
Bar leverages body weight to lock in doorways without drilling or screws and supports up to 300 pounds. Assembly is quick and easy with tools included 
Quality construction supports the results you want 
Doorway pull up bars have rightfully earned the respect of fitness enthusiasts. Great workouts at home start with a pull up bar ready to go at a moment's notice. The addition of the elevated bar extends your range of motion for the kind of performance you expect from the mounted bars at the gym. 
To handle the added leverage of the elevated bar, the Ultimate Body Press XL Pull Up Bar uses the thickest steel, quality hardware and our exclusive ABS couplers so each crossbar can be properly tightened and locked at 90° to the uprights. You feel the difference on the wall and the XL Doorway Bar retains it's shape under strenuous floor exercises. 
The elevated doorway bar that supports your confidence leaves you free to focus on form and repetition for the results you want in less time. 
Expand your Workouts with Floor Exercises and Optional Accessories 
Add a new challenge to push ups with the Elevated Pull Up Bar in the floor position. High density grips extend your endurance and help keep your focus on form and repetition. 
Dips Get the Upper Body Results You Want - Fast. 
Dips rapidly build chest, arms, back and core. Get the look and performance you want targeting the triceps, lats, traps and pecs. 
Perfect Support for Sit Ups 
The Elevated Doorway Pull Up Bar locks into your lower doorway for fully supported sit ups. 
Anchor Optional Pull Up Bar Accessories 
Add optional Ab Straps and Gymnastic Rings to transform your Doorway Pull Up Bar into a complete home gym. Pull up bar accessories expand your favorite exercises with new compound movements and increase your rep counts to full sets with assisted exercise variations. If you are seeking a performance edge on the field, working up to your first pull up or rediscovering your best performance levels, pull up bar accessories get comprehensive results fast. (accessories sold separately)

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
SPORTIC is a vibrant brand specializing in body exercise equipment and aims at encouraging more people to find a better exercise method and get a better bodyshape. We are striving for exploring more efficient and exciting exercise equipment, so this new chin up bar comes out. 
This pull up bar requires no stool and it is quite convenient to change the places for exercise. Firstly please connect the 3-section parts together. Then you could rotate the middle rod to extend or shorten the length to your need. 
Sportic strength training chin up bar without screws is an efficient, convenient, practical and affordable product. Be sure to check whether the pull-up bar and your door frame are in intact condition before use. Once it is installed correctly, it will be solid enough for strenghth training. 
This creative bubble level is quite useful for quick assembly. When the length of this pull up bar is adjusted to the doorframe, and just check the position of the bubble. That part is small and clear, so it is easy to be sure whether it is horizontal. If it is horizontal, it is ready for use. 
This door pull up bar will help exercise different body parts. It is designed for burning calories to maintain the figure and help circulation improvement. It is assembled with no damage to your door frame, so it is easier to adjust the exercise plan according to your needs.
