title: Kipika 48" Ceiling Mounted Pull Up Bar, Heavy Duty Multi-Grip Chin Up Bar,Mounted Pull Up Bar, Adjustable Height, Pull Up Bands for Chin Ups & Body Stretching, Ideal for Home Gym and Strength Training
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
features: 【Five Grip Styles for Versatile Workouts】Our pull-up bar has five grip styles: wide grip, narrow grip, neutral grip, chin-up grip, and hammer grip. You can switch between these grips to complete many different workouts and stimulate different parts of your back, arms, and lats. You can also challenge yourself with different variations of pull-ups, such as L-sit pull-ups, muscle-ups, or weighted pull-ups.

【Adjustable Height】The height of the support arms can be adjusted in five positions, and the distance from the mounting surface can be adjusted from 18 inches to 26 inches. This means you can customize your pull-up bar to fit your space and preference.

【Durable and Rust-Resistant Material】Our pull-up bar is made of high quality material with black metal powder coating, which makes it rust and scratch resistant, and suitable for indoor or outdoor use. Whether you want to work out in your garage, basement, backyard or gym, this pull-up bar can be mounted securely and safely on any suitable surface.

【Easy Installation】Our pull-up bar comes with all the mounting screws you need, including wood screws for mounting on wood and pull-pop screws for mounting on concrete walls. The mounting holes are spaced 48 inches apart to accommodate ceiling studs spaced 12 inches and 24 inches apart, and the mounting base is 2.2 inches wide, perfect for studs 2 inches and up.
【Stable and Secure Support】Our pull-up bar is very stable and secure. Each support foot has four mounting hole positions.
【Satisfaction Guarantee】If you are not SATISFIED with our ceiling Pull Up Bar for any reason, be free to contact our 24 h-support services.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Commercial Wall Mounted Pull Up Bar 
WEIGHT CAPACITY 
Built to support up to 850 lbs, this pull-up bar offers exceptional strength and durability, ensuring reliable performance for users of all sizes and workout intensities. 
EXTENDED RANGE 
Designed for unrestricted movement, this pull-up bar extends 22.5 inches from the wall, providing plenty of space for pull-ups, muscle-ups, and dynamic workouts. 
MULTI-GRIP 
Elevate your workout with this versatile pull-up bar featuring 14 knurled grips for optimal comfort and control. Designed for a variety of grip positions, it allows targeted muscle engagement. 
SECURITY INCLUDED 
Featuring 8 heavy-duty 3-inch lag screws, this pull-up bar mounts securely to wooden studs, ensuring maximum stability and safety during intense workouts. 
28MM GRIP 
Featuring a 28mm diameter grip, this pull-up bar offers an optimal balance of comfort and control, ensuring a secure hold during every workout. 
HEAVY CONTRUCTION 
Built with heavy-duty materials and reinforced welds, this pull-up bar offers unmatched strength and durability, ensuring reliable performance for even the most intense workouts. 
Width 	50.25" (Mounts to 48" studs centered) 	
Height 	23.75" 	
Depth 	23" (Front of Bar is 22.25") 	
Inner Grip Width 	7" 	
Weight Capacity 	850 lbs 	
Knurled Grip Positions 	14 	
Bar Diameter 	28mm 	
Material 	Powder Coated Steel 	
Mounting Hardware 	Included 	
What is the weight capacity of the pull-up bar? 
The pull-up bar supports up to 850 lbs, providing strong and reliable support for a wide range of users. 
What type of mounting hardware is included? 
(8) 3" lag screws are included 
Can I use a suspension trainer with this pull-up bar? 
Yes, suspension trainers can be hooked to the pull-up bar, allowing for a wide range of full-body exercises, including rows, push-ups, and core workouts. Unit must be properly mounted. 
Can this pull-up bar be installed on drywall? 
No, the pull-up bar should be installed on wooden studs with the included hardware for maximum stability and safety. 
Does the pull-up bar require professional installation? 
While it can be installed by most users, professional installation is recommended for those unfamiliar with mounting equipment securely.

From the manufacturer
Stamina Power Tower 1690 
Building total body strength and sculpting your chest, abs, back and arms has never been easier or more convenient. The Stamina 1690 Power Tower provides total body workout, suitable for body strengthening, losing weight, building and toning muscles. This pull up bar station helps improve your figure, posture, mobility, balance and overall fitness. 
With the Stamina 1690 Power Tower, you’ll get a whole lot of gym equipment in one 49” by 42” footprint. 
Convenient home fitness | For full body strengthening 
The Stamina Power Tower 1960 is one piece of equipment with multiple workout stations for push-ups, pull-ups, sit-ups, tricep dips, and vertical knee raises. The 1690 Power Tower is free standing with a small footprint, so it fits easily into your home workout area, providing an intense yet safe workout. 
One piece of equipment | Multiple workout stations 
This versatile dip station offers different workout possibilities. Its multiple workout stations utilize gravity and your own body weight to provide an invigorating, effective workout. There's a push-up station, a pull-up station, triceps dips station, and sit-up station. The durable steel frame of this free standing pull up bar supports users of up to 250 lbs. 
Comfort and stability 
This dip bar tower is designed for users with limited space. The dip handles have comfortable, grippable foam padding, while ankle pads provide comfort for sit-ups. The push-up and pull-up stations padded grips, keep hands from slipping. The heavy duty steel tube frame is sturdy and solid, the powdered coated finish is scratch resistant. 
Experience connected fitness with this home gym equipment with the müüv app. With smart guided coaching, exercise demo videos, personalized workouts, assembly videos, and more, müüv provides the best workout and fitness experience with your Stamina equipment. features: 【Super Strong. Super Durable.】Sportsroyals power tower is a pull up bar with excellent performance and an amazing 400 lbs load capacity. It is the first choice for those who pursue professional fitness quality.

From Monday to Friday, you will have new challenges every day.

There are also 5 levels of backrest adjustment, which can fit different body curves closely and provide precise support for the waist and back. It can be easily adjusted to meet the fitness needs of the whole family and realize a new model of home gym sharing.

【Designed for Your Ultimate Comfort】Sportsroyals chin up bar incorporates ergonomic design into every detail.The auxiliary pad is filled with high-quality foam to fit the arm and relieve pressure; the 10-degree inclined armrests reduce the risk of joint wear and muscle strain; the high-density rubber non-slip grip allows for a firm grip even when sweating. From comfort to stability to safety, it has professional quality in every aspect and is a perfect choice for your home gym.

【Min Footprint, Max Versatility】The space-saving power tower only occupies 9.8 square inches, which does not take up too much living space and fits perfectly into family life. The compact design of the parallel bars can be easily moved between the corner of the living room and the balcony. No matter where you are, you can start your fitness moment and provide you with professional and efficient exercise in a limited space.

【3 Steps Quick Assembly】The power tower gym comes with clear instructions, intuitive installation video help, and ready-made professional installation tools.The installation process is simple and orderly. Firstly,easily install the base; in the second step, start installing the handrails, and finally install the pull-up bar. Once completed, you can start your fitness journey.

【Ideal for Full Body Muscle Building】Owning it is like having a personal trainer who can help you exercise your whole body at home. Sportsroyals pull-up bar is not just a machine , but also a muscle sculpting master. From full chest muscles to well-defined calves, a few simple actions can easily create a good body.No longer have to endure the noisy gym, let's start the journey of fitness and body shaping at home.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
TOPOKO Pull Up Bar for Doorway lets you set up a versatile home gym with ease. 
Whether you're working from home, a student, or a busy parent, the TOPOKO doorway pull up bar is your perfect workout partner. It helps you build muscle, burn fat, and stay fit—all from the comfort of home, whenever you have time. 
Built with heavy-duty steel, the TOPOKO chin up bar is strong and stable for all your workouts. It has thick foam pads to protect your wall and ergonomic, non-slip handles for a comfortable grip—keeping your doorframe safe while you exercise. 
Upgrade your home workouts with the TOPOKO Pull Up Bar for Doorway. With three grip positions—narrow, wide, and neutral—you can target your shoulders, biceps, chest, back, and core. Ideal for pull-ups, push-ups, dips, sit-ups, and more, it helps you build strength and tone your upper body. 
This doorway pull up bar is built with 1.7mm heavy-duty steel for strength and stability. It has thick foam pads to protect your wall and ergonomic foam handles for a comfortable, non-slip grip. Durable and wear-resistant, it provides a stable workout while keeping your doorframe scratch-free. 
Installing the TOPOKO Pull-Up Bar is quick and easy. With the included manual and tool, you can set it up in any standard doorway (23" to 31" wide, 4.7" to 7.5" deep). Its lever design requires no drilling, so your door stays damage-free. 
For customers who speak Spanish-Para los clientes que hablan español. 
Fabricada con acero de alta resistencia,barra para hacer ejercicio TOPOKO garantiza robustez y estabilidad durante tus entrenamientos. La parte superior de acero cuadrado cuenta con tiras de espuma gruesa para proteger la pared, mientras que los mangos ergonómicos de espuma cómoda aseguran un agarre antideslizante y cómodo, mejorando tu experiencia de ejercicio y previniendo daños en el marco de la puerta. 
Instalar la barra de dominadas TOPOKO es muy sencillo. Con un manual de ensamblaje y herramienta incluidos, puedes configurarla rápidamente en cualquier puerta estándar de 23" a 31" de ancho, con una profundidad de 4.7" a 7.5". Gracias a su innovador diseño de palanca, no se requiere perforación, asegurando que tu puerta permanezca intacta.

title: Ally Peaks Pull Up Bar for Doorway | Thickened Steel Max Limit 440 lbs Upper Body Fitness Workout Bar| Multi-Grip Strength for Doorway | Indoor Chin-Up Bar Fitness Trainer for Home Gym Portable |180
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Pull-Up Bars
features: 💪 HEAVY DUTY CONSTRUCTION: The pull up bar make of 1.7mm thickened refined heavy steel and the fine powder coating prevent rust and corrosion.Upgraded 2024 THICKER GRADE 8.8 Ally Peaks exclusive bolts( PASSED A 2200 POUND LOAD BEARING TEST) and high quality lock nuts make sure the bar never gets loose. It is much better than ordinary one just for the extra safety .It can hold up to 440 pounds. And the handles are coated with high fiber foam, comfortable grip, multi-function, anti-slip and wear resistance.

💪 MULTI-FUNCTION HOME GYM: We present you an extra resistance bands set with high quality,Package includes 2*resistance bands(1 for 30lb &1 for 25lb),2*handles,1*Door Anchor.Target multiple upper body & core muscles with pull-ups, push-ups, dips, and hanging crunches, multiple functions replace all other equipment.With this pull up bar, home and office become your gym and you can do exercises in a quick way.

💪UPGRADED DOUBLE SILICONE PROTECTION FOR DOOR FRAME:We have upgraded the traditional foam that contacts the door frame to elastic silicone material.Permanent use,better fits and protects door frame without marks.In addition,the chin up bar comes with a pair of extra 4mm No-Trace removable silicone pads .Why do we add protective pads?Because when we do exercise there is an upward and downward force of friction.So double silicone protection(double insurance)for your door frame is the best way.

💪 EASY TO USE DOORWAY PULL UP BAR: Portable design for home exercise pull-ups - can be mounted on any standard 24 "to 32" doorways,depth of 4.7"-8.27",Acceptable trim height up to 3.75"，fits on any standard doorway. Door frame pull up bar uses leverage to hold against the doorway so there are no screws and no damage to door and easy to install and remove.

💪 PIONEERING TWO-LEVEL ADJUSTABLE DESIGN:Unique double hole design on the bend of the pull up bar precisely matches door frames of different thicknesses.Through extensive sample testing, we found that a single hole cannot perfectly and accurately match all different thicknesses of door frames, but for a 25-diameter iron pipe，higher density of holes would compromise the sturdiness of the handle, posing safety risks during usage. Therefore, after extensive data analysis, we have chosen two appropriate holes for our doorway pull up bar. This design ensures both precise matching for the majority of door frame thicknesses and product durability. It has been validated by over 100,000 customers.

💪 SECURE & SAFE: Simple and easy to install or uninstall and store when there is limited space. Heavy-duty chrome steel doorway pulls up bar and door mounts provide great support and safety. Before using the upper body workout bar tug down on the grips to make sure the unit is securely installed into door frame.

💪 180-Days Free Return:For any questions or problems contact us via Amazon.We reply promptly to all inquiries and will solve it for you as soon as possible. We also offer a 180 day money back guarantee.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Ally Peaks pull up bar 
Experience The Difference 
OUR GOAL: Provide advanced products to improve your life. 
Let us start your training with Ally Peaks. 
Everytime we try our best to make our product better.And we insist on using the best materials for our products.Because we hope you will be happy when you receive our products and it is helpful for you.Our greatest wish is that you will feel secure and happy when you use our products.AND OUR DISTINGUISHED CUSTOMER ARE WORTH IT. 
SIX CHARACTERISTICS OF OUR PULL UP BAR FOR DOORWAY 
THICKENED STEEL PIPE SUPER HEAVY DUTY 
The doorway pull up bar is made of 1.7MM Thickened steel support up to 440LBS 
HIGH QUALITY LOCK NUTS 
Upgraded 2024 THICKER GRADE 8.8 Ally Peaks exclusive bolts which PASSED A 2200 POUND LOAD BEARING TEST. 
High quality Stainless Self-Locking Nylon Insert make sure the bar never gets loose. 
BE MORE SECURE 
STURDY PREMIUM CONSTRUCTION 
All parts of pull up bar are made of thickened refined heavy steel+High-density foams .In order to cut cost,some ordinary doorway pull up bar’s this part are made of hollow plastic,this part will not strong enough（It will age and deform or even fracture after a long time）.
Protruding fixing point design let the bar more secure and more beautiful.
Upgraded double silicone protection for door frame 1/2 
All customers who have purchased the same type of doorway pull-up bar will find that the foam(between the door frame and the bar) is damaged after a short time of use without exception, then damage the door frame. It causes great annoyance to users. 
In order to completely eliminate this situation, we creatively upgraded our pull up bar to a full circle of ultra-thick elastic silicone protective covers. It can perfectly match and protect the door frame while being used permanently. 
Upgraded double silicone protection for door frame 2/2 
The chin up bar comes with a pair of extra 4mm No-Trace removable silicone pads.Why are we still equipped with extra silicone pads for this pull up bar?Because we find that when we do exercise there is not only an inward force on the door frame but also an upward and downward force of friction.So double silicone protection(double insurance) is the best way to permanently prevent the bar damage to door frame. 
SUPPLEMENTARY TRAINING 
Considering when you don't have enough strength to do pull-up after some training,we present you an extra resistance bands set with high quality as a supplementary training,Package includes 2*resistance bands(1 for 30lb &1 for 25lb),2*handles,1*Door Anchor. 
YOU CAN DO SOME TRAINING ABOUT YOU BACK.THIS RESISTANCE BANDS LET YOUR TRAINING EASIER. 

SUPER HEAVY DUTY PULL UP BAR FOR DOORWAY 
SUPPLEMENTARY TRAINING 
You can use the resistance bands as your supplementary training.When you do not have enough strength after you do some training,you can continue training with those resistance bands.The fitness effect will be more obvious both of them are used together. 
Resistance bands package includes 2*resistance bands(1 for 30lb &1 for 25lb),2*handles,1*Door Anchor. 
Can do some training for back, shoulders, chest, arms, legs,triceps, biceps and so on 
MULTI-FUNCTION HOME GYM 
THICKENED SSTEEL PULL UP BAR SUPPORT UP TO 440LBS 
Begin to plan your home workout and unlock their full with Ally Peaks pull up bar.Let every door be your personal gym.The doorway pull up bar with three grip positions, narrow, wide, and neutral.Target multiple upper body & core muscles with pull-ups, push-ups, dips, and sit-ups.With this pull up bar, home and office become your gym.High fiber material foams on the grips let your workout more comfortable.Powerful double protection system for the door frame make your workout more secure. 
The door pull up bar can be used on 24 "to 32" width and 4.7 "to 7.5"depth door frame.PLEASE CHECK YOUR DOOR FRAME BEFORE ORDERING 
Please stick the protection pads on the door frame where the frame and the bar are in contact to protect your door frame

All customers who have purchased the same type of doorway pull-up bar will find that the foam(between the door frame and the bar) is damaged after a short time of use without exception, then damage the door frame. It causes great annoyance to users. 
In order to completely eliminate this situation, we creatively upgraded our pull up bar to a full circle of ultra-thick elastic silicone protective covers. It can perfectly match and protect the door frame while being used permanently. 
Upgraded double silicone protection for door frame 2/2 
The chin up bar comes with a pair of extra 4mm No-Trace removable silicone pads.Why are we still equipped with extra silicone pads for this pull up bar?Because we find that when we do exercise there is not only an inward force on the door frame but also an upward and downward force of friction.So double silicone protection(double insurance) is the best way to permanently prevent the bar damage to door frame.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Pull Up Bar with Support Frame —— MAX LOAD BEARING 1100LBS! 
Why Do We Need a Pull Up Bar At Home? 
For better workouts every day! 
You can create your own indoor gym this winter! 
If you want to improve your fitness, this is a good choice for you! 
This pull up bar exists to inspire active, healthy lifestyles with products that make fitness attainable and enjoyable for everyone! 
Pull Up Bar and Chin Up Bar with Support Frame 
You can create your own indoor gym! Pull-up bars are perfect for pull-ups, chin-ups, sit-ups, dips, crunches, triceps dips, leg raises and more. Easy to carry it and hassle-free to install. No need go to gym to waste your time, just start your workout at home or office any time! 
Specifications 
Bar Length: 30.7''~37.4''(78cm-95cm)
Material: Steel Tube, EVA Foam, Rubber
Max Load: 1100 lbs (500kg)
Safety Tips: 
Do not jump up to grab the pull up bar. 
Minors should use the bar under the supervision of a guardian. 
It is forbidden to use the doorway pull up bar to stand upside down and other dangerous actions. 
Details 
Anti-Skid Device 
Anti-skid device on both sides, which can firmly stick on the wall.when pull the bar,It will spread the gravity to both sides.So have higher slip resistance ,ensures stability. 
Prevent from sliding 
Safety buckle device, Lock the pull up bar according to the prompt direction, rotate to tight, make exercise more secure. 
Support Frame 
LADER pull up bar is equipped with support frame! When mounted properly, this fitness bar can hold up to 1100lbs(500kg), giving you full support for pull ups and chin ups. 
Comfortable Grips 
Comfort Grips Minimize risks of calluses or hand cramping with padded handles.Deodorant, sweat absorbing, tear resistant, and can prevent the rod metal from being corroded by sweat. 
Multi-Purpose Home Pull Up Bar 
Sit-up 
It can exercise the muscles of the waist and abdomen. 
Push-up 
It can exercise the muscles of the pectoral, waist and abdomen. 
Stretching exercise 
It can exercise your body flexibility and warm-up exercises before exercise. 
Pull-up 
It can exercise the upper body muscles, mainly training latissimus dorsi.

Easy to carry and install: The pull up auxiliary strap is equipped with a high-quality compact storage bag, which has excellent portability. aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer

4 ergonomic grip positions including 20" neutral grip spacing support better workouts every day. 
Better Workouts Every Day 
The Ceiling Mount Pull Up Bar features a state of the art combination of grip angles previously available only on commercial gym equipment. 
By providing a more natural hand position during chin ups, parallel grip and wide grip pullups, the finely tuned angled grips help you avoid over articulation of the shoulders and reduce strain on your wrists and elbows. 
4 padded grip positions 
ideal 20" neutral grip spacing 
Ultra stable rigid mount 
Full range of motion for every exercise 
The Ceiling Mount Pull Up Bar 
With Patented Dual Position Risers 
The Ceiling Mount Pull Up Bar with Reversible Risers by Ultimate Body Press fits 16" and 24" ceiling joists and is ergonomically designed to reduce strain and increase gains during your pullup workouts. 
Featuring ideal 20" spacing on the parallel grips and angled bars for a more natural grip position, the Ceiling Mount Pull Up Bar targets specific muscle groups for the results you want in less time. Complete hardware, mounting template and instructions are included for easy installation. 
Hardware, template and instructions for easy mounting 
Order with confidence and get better workouts every day 
Patented Dual Position Risers 
The Ceiling Mount Pull Up Bar features our patented innovation – Reversible Dual Position Risers. Whether you are installing below floor joists spaced 16" on-center or ceiling joists with 24" on-center spacing, the reversible Dual Position Risers allow mounting where you want it to best preserve valuable floor space for expanded exercises with bar accessories. 
Comfortably spaced at 20", the parallel grips are a great fit for just about every build and are ideally spaced for chin ups. The bar drops 14" from your ceiling providing plenty of head room and a full range of motion for all of your favorite pull up variations. 
Position I 
Fits below standard 16 inch on-center floor joist. 
US Patent: 9.427,611 B11 - 8/2016. 
Position II 
Fits below standard 24 inch on-center ceiling joists. 
Ideal Grip Spacing 
Both riser positions feature 20 inch spacing on the neutral grips for an ideal fit for just about every build. 14 inch riser height provides full range of motion for every pull up variation.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Ultra Fuego wall mount pull-up bar is newly upgraded, which help you carry out full body workout to achieve your fitness aims easily and efficiently! 
Compared with conventional pull-up bars, this gym bar has stable and solid overall structure. Adding three eyelets, it is available for you to hang up punching bag, resistance bands or TRX straps for your training, which works best on your back, biceps, chest, shoulders, arms, and abdominal muscles! 
Ultra Fuego pull-up bar is sturdy and especially suitable for people or gym owners who are looking for a very stable indoor bar with high load-bearing capacity. 

Ultra Fuego is devoted to researching, developing and producing home sports equipment. In search of excellence, we strive to supply premium products and continuously optimize product details. Whether at home, in the garage or basement, we hope our customers can find the suitable products , build an ideal home gym and achieve their fitness goals. Please stay tuned for more new products from Ultra Fuego! 
Advantages over competitors 
Thicken steel pipe construction and cross-strutting support, particularly sturdy
5-in 1 Multi function wall mounted chin up bar,easy to stay fit and home workout
Different grip position offer you flexible exercise
3 eyelets to attach additional training equipment
8 heavy-duty expansion bolts included
Mounting Type : Wall mounted 
Safe to use up to 300lbs. 
Package Weight: 16.95 lbs 
Item Dimensions LxWxH：38.4*25.2*8.86 inches 
The quality is superb, it's solid and well built with nice neat welds and comfortable hand holds.
It came with expansion bolts fitted which ARE absolutely fit for purpose and hold the apparatus in place with no problems whatsoever. The hook for the punch bag are an added AMAZING design. Also This hook to use resistance band, hence making it a multi gym set up.
You can install it indoors or outdoors. To have this installed in your garden away from prying eyes is doing wonders for your upper body strength.
Up to 300lbs Weight Capacity 
Ultra Fuego pull up bar can support up to 300lbs, which is suitable for most fitness enthusiasts to achieve fitness goals. It is ideal for whole family use as well. 
More Training Possibilities Available 
Three extra hooks are added for you to hung up punch bag, TRX straps, resistance bands etc., which can provide you with more training possibilities. 
Handles with High-grade Rubbery Foam 
Anti-slip foam sleeves are attached to the handles, which absorb sweat of your hands so that possible injuries can be prevented from happening and you can do workout free from worry. 
Commercial Grade Heavy-duty Steel 
In order to make it solid, strong and sturdy enough to assist your training, the whole pull up bar is made of heavy steel with a thickness of 1.5mm. 
Triangular Base Structure 
The steel tubes form a triangle structure along with the base frame, which make the pull up bar more stable and able to have higher load-bearing capacity. 
A Cross Beam Added 
In order to well spread the load on the front part of the pull up bar, a cross beam is added to connect the two dip bars. The H-shaped frame boosts the overall safety and stabillity of the pull up bar, which help the user to do workout efficiently.

Whether at home, in the garage or basement, we hope our customers can find the suitable products , build an ideal home gym and achieve their fitness goals. Please stay tuned for more new products from Ultra Fuego!

The quality is superb, it's solid and well built with nice neat welds and comfortable hand holds.
It came with expansion bolts fitted which ARE absolutely fit for purpose and hold the apparatus in place with no problems whatsoever. The hook for the punch bag are an added AMAZING design. Also This hook to use resistance band, hence making it a multi gym set up.
You can install it indoors or outdoors. To have this installed in your garden away from prying eyes is doing wonders for your upper body strength.

aiReviewsSummary.text: Customers are satisfied with the pull up bar's build quality and sturdiness. They find it well-built and easy to install.
